<%= render 'pages/header' %>

<div class="background_info">
What do you get that person that has everything? <br><br>  That new thing, they’ve got it. A trip, they’ve been. Cash, come on now. So why not give them something that is both precious to you and the recipient; time, your time, The Gift of Time. <br><br>

By pledging your time on behalf of another, you hit three things that make a truly impactful gift: <br><br>

    Personalization: You give a unique, selfless gift to a social cause important to the receiver<br>
   Use of resources: While usually measured in $$, personal resources are often valued much more<br>
    Effort: Proof of planning and effort are required, and they’ll recognize that!<br><br>
    To help get the most of these elements, please answer the questions below as thoroughly as possible, and then get started! (…and don’t forget to upload a picture of yourself doing it!)
<div class="ui inverted divider"></div>
</div>

<div class="ui form center_form">

    <%= form_for @gift do |f| %>
        <div class="field">
            <%= f.label :recipient_name, 'Who are you donating your time for?' %>
            <%= f.text_field :recipient_name, placeholder: 'Full name' %>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
            <%= f.label :relationship_to_gifter, 'Relationship' %>
            <select id='gift_relationship_to_gifter' name='gift[relationship_to_gifter]'>
                <option class="item" value="Mother/Father">Mother/Father</option>
                <option class="item" value="Brother/Sister">Brother/Sister</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Aunt/Uncle">Aunt/Uncle</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Cousin">Cousin</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Friend">Friend</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Mentor">Mentor</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Significant other">Significant other</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Significant other">Other</option> 
            </select>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
             <%= f.label :cause, 'To what cause are you donating your time?' %>
            <select id='gift_cause' name='gift[cause]'>
                <option class="item" value="Academia, Learning and Skills Development">Academia, Learning and Skills Development</option>
                <option class="item" value="Alcoholism and Drug Abuse">Addiction</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Racism">Anti-Racism</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Animal Rights">Animal Rights</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Children's Support and Rights">Children's Support and Rights</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Civil Rights">Civil Rights</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Community Involvement">Community Involvement</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Disaster Support">Disaster Support</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Education">Education</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Elderly">Elderly</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Environmental">Environmental</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Homeless/Poverty">Homeless/Poverty</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Human Rights">Human Rights</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Illness - Research and Awareness">Illness - Research and Awareness</option> 
                <option class="item" value="International Aid">International Aid</option> 
                <option class="item" value="LGBT">LGBT Rights</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Mental Health">Mental Health</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Pay it Forward - Act of Kindness">Pay it Forward - Act of Kindness</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Political">Political</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Religious">Religious</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Women's Rights">Women's Rights</option> 
                <option class="item" value="Other">Other</option> 
            </select>           
        </div>
        <div class="field">
            <%= f.label :other_cause, 'If other, what cause?' %>
            <%= f.text_field :other_cause %>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
            <%= f.label :description, 'Describe the volunteer act you will perform' %>
            <%= f.text_area :description %>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
            <%= f.label :organization, 'Which organization will you donate your time to?' %>
            <%= f.text_field :organization %>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
            <%= f.label :expected_hours, 'How many hours do you expect to donate?' %>
            <%= f.text_field :expected_hours %>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
            <%= f.label :expected_completion_date, 'When do you expect to complete your hours?' %>
            <%= f.text_field :expected_completion_date %>
        </div>
        <%= f.submit 'Create design', class: 'ui tiny button', id: 'create_gift' %>
    <% end %>
</div>